The '''Ralltiiri''', '''Ralltireans''', or '''Ralltiirians'''<ref name="ITCW">{{JournalCite|7|Into the Core Worlds}}</ref> were natives of the [[Core Worlds/Legends|Core World]] [[Ralltiir/Legends|Ralltiir]]. Ralltiiri natives included [[Pharl McQuarrie/Legends|Pharl McQuarrie]], [[Yerka Mig]], [[Derek Klivian/Legends|Derek Klivian]], [[Retwin]], and [[Jeroen Webb]].

